It was also the foundation of Watson's carefully built corporate culture.
"For us at IBM, long-term thinking is a continuous movement towards the future.
IBM survived and prospered for a century by staying true to its core values while not being afraid to change everything else around it.
This allowed us to transform technology, business and society during our first centuries.
We hope to achieve even more in the second hundred," said samuel J. Palmisano, the company's current ceo, on the anniversary.
Sophisticated system
